From: agruen@suse.de
Subject: permanent temporary hotfix for SuSE kernels

This is a temporary hotfix that allows to use 2.6 kernels for Autobuild.
Chris Mason <mason@suse.de> is expected to look into this in week 49
(Dec 1-5).


